content:
Work More Intuitively with Record Rollup Definitions UI

Create record rollup definitions with just a few clicks by using an easy-to-use and intuitive UI. Use the record rollup definitions to aggregate records from multiple objects or groups according to your business requirements.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience of multiple Industries clouds.

Why: Business executives often struggle to make informed decisions because the data is scattered across different objects.

How: From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Rollup Definitions, and then select Record Rollup Definitions. To create a record rollup definition, click New Rollup Definition.
title: Work More Intuitively with Record Rollup Definitions
